# Technology Stack Requirements

## Core Technologies
- react-router@7.1.5 (framework mode)
  - Documentation: https://reactrouter.com/home
  - Don't import from 'react-router-dom' or '@remix-run', it's outdated
- shadcn@latest
  - Documentation: https://ui.shadcn.com/docs
- react-hook-form@7.54.2
- @hookform/resolvers with zod
- zod@3.24.2
- remix-utils@8.1.0

## Package Management
- Use pnpm as package manager
- Always refer to package.json for:
  - Package versions
  - Import methods
  - Dependencies

## UI Components
- Use shadcn/ui components
- Follow shadcn/ui installation and usage guidelines

## Library Usage
- Before implementing custom solutions, check for suitable existing libraries
- Prioritize maintained and well-documented libraries